  "market_context": "Daily chart of crude oil (CL1!) showing a candle two closure forming after a swing low. The closure is not located at a defined point of interest, raising a validation concern for treating it as a tradable swing.",
  "key_observation": "Although the candle two closure does not occur at a point of interest, the correlated asset RB is simultaneously reaching into a fair value gap, creating an SMT divergence that validates the swing point and allows continuation trading higher.",
  "analysis_steps": [
    "Step 1: Identify the candle two closure forming on the daily chart but note it is not at a defined point of interest.",
    "Step 2: Cross-reference the correlated asset RB at the same time and observe that RB is reaching into a fair value gap.",
    "Step 3: Recognize this discrepancy as an SMT divergence which validates the candle two as a swing point despite the absence of a POI.",
    "Step 4: Treat the setup as valid for continuation trading higher off the swing low."
  ],
